com.wedriveu.mobile.service.vehicle

Interface VehicleService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    VehicleServiceImpl

    public interface VehicleService
    Service that manages all vehicle remote communications, so it exposes the capability of subscribing and unsubscribing to all the main vehicle events like: updates, entering, arrived at destination and substitution.
